{%- comment -%}
  Icon Component

  This snippet renders various SVG icons based on the provided icon name.
  Usage:
  {% render 'icons', icon: 'arrow-down' %}
  {% render 'icons', icon: 'search', width: 32, height: 32 %}
  {% render 'icons', icon: 'cart', width: 20 %}
  Parameters:
  icon (required): The name of the icon to render
  width (optional): Width of the icon in pixels (default: 24)
  height (optional): Height of the icon in pixels (default: 24)
  Available Icons:
  Navigation: arrow-down, arrow-up, arrow-left, arrow-right, arrow-down-left,
  arrow-up-left, arrow-down-right, arrow-up-right, chevron-down,
  chevron-left, chevron-right, chevron-up
  Actions: add, subtract, close, filter, search, trash, play
  Social: facebook, instagram, tiktok, youtube, linkedin
  Commerce: cart, account, account-circle, mail
  UI: info, lock, bulb, star-check, truck, search-star, eye, hamburger,
  question, warning-circle, warning, dotted-circle, star, check-circle
  Badges: privacy-choice, new, new-badge, confetti, fire
  Special: subscription, gift, call, sync, message, locator, stretch
  Safety Features: slip-oil-resistant, electric-hazard, heat-resistant,
  puncture-resistant, astm-2413, astm-2892, water-proof,
  water-resistant, safety-toe, brunt-usa-flag, dollar, box
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign icon_width = width | default: 24
  assign icon_height = height | default: 24
-%}

